Hey guys. Well I just recently changed my maximum level from 99, to 135.

The problem I'm having, is that whenever I try make my stats level 135, the maximum it goes to is 126 and stops at 200M xp. I would like the maximum xp to be 500M, so that it can actually reach level 135.

This is my current method if it helps:
[code]
	public int getLevelForXP(int exp) {
		int points = 0;
		int output = 0;
		if (exp > 500000001)
			return 135;
		for (int lvl = 1; lvl <= 135; lvl++) {
			points += Math.floor((double) lvl + 300.0
					* Math.pow(2.0, (double) lvl / 7.0));
			output = (int) Math.floor(points / 4);
			if (output >= exp) {
				return lvl;
			}
		}
		return 0;
	}
